{"id": "art-436", "label": "Art. 436", "title": "Art. 436: Declararea recursului în casaţie", "slug": "art-436", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_570043248\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1610\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_570043248\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 436:\nDeclararea recursului în casa&#355;ie </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_312155147\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1609\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_312155147\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pot formula\ncerere de recurs în casa&#355;ie:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1949648463\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1608\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1949648463\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)procurorul, în ceea ce prive&#351;te latura penal&#259;\n&#351;i latura civil&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1018281955\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1607\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1018281955\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)inculpatul, în ceea ce prive&#351;te latura penal&#259;\n&#351;i latura civil&#259;, împotriva hot&#259;rârilor prin care s-a dispus\ncondamnarea, renun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei sau amânarea aplic&#259;rii\npedepsei ori încetarea procesului penal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_916540647\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1606\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_916540647\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)partea civil&#259; &#351;i partea responsabil&#259;\ncivilmente, în ceea ce prive&#351;te latura civil&#259;, iar referitor la\nlatura penal&#259;, în m&#259;sura în care solu&#355;ia din aceast&#259;\nlatur&#259; a influen&#355;at solu&#355;ia în latura civil&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_620783704\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1605\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_620783704\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2036531531\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1604\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2036531531\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>[textul din Art. 436, alin. (2) din partea 2, titlul III,\ncapitolul V, sectiunea 2 a fost abrogat la 31-oct-2016 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul 2. din Ordonanta urgenta 70/2016</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_260158224\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1603\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_260158224\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pân&#259; la închiderea dezbaterilor la instan&#355;a de\nrecurs, p&#259;r&#355;ile &#351;i procurorul î&#351;i pot retrage recursul în\ncasa&#355;ie declarat. Retragerea trebuie s&#259; fie f&#259;cut&#259; personal\nde parte sau prin mandatar special, iar dac&#259; partea se afl&#259; în stare\nde de&#355;inere, printr-o declara&#355;ie atestat&#259; sau consemnat&#259;\nîntr-un proces-verbal de c&#259;tre conducerea locului de de&#355;inere.\nDeclara&#355;ia de retragere se poate face fie la instan&#355;a a c&#259;rei\nhot&#259;râre a fost atacat&#259;, fie la instan&#355;a de recurs.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1259103420\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1602\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1259103420\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Reprezentan&#355;ii legali pot retrage recursul în\ncasa&#355;ie cu respectarea, în ceea ce prive&#351;te latura civil&#259;, a\ncondi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute de legea civil&#259;. Inculpatul minor nu poate\nretrage recursul în casa&#355;ie declarat personal sau de reprezentantul\ns&#259;u legal.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_732925922\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1601\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_732925922\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Recursul în casa&#355;ie declarat de procuror poate fi\nretras de procurorul ierarhic superior.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1653940936\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1600\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1653940936\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Decizia instan&#355;ei de apel prin care a fost respins\napelul nu poate fi atacat&#259; cu recurs în casa&#355;ie de persoanele care nu\nau exercitat calea de atac a apelului ori când apelul acestora a fost retras.</span></p>"}